Copy of 2D game from RyiSnow @youtube re-created here for learning.

The organization of the game code:
source
main package
	-game main method for the game and creates jframe and adds gamepanel to the frame
	-gamepanel most of the methods logic are here
	-keyhandler controller 
	
entity package
	-entity
	-player
	
tile package
	-tilemanager
	-tile

resources
maps package

player package

tiles package